metadata.description: Kilgores are a group of holiday-only characters who provide collectors with access to the best NFTs and Experiential Utilities in the NFT industry. This release is surrounded by Kilgores, Halloween-themed characters designed by Music Artist and Social Media Influencer Justen Kilgore and issued as NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain to celebrate Kil-Gore-Ween. The first 10,000 Kilgores will be created using a wide range of costumes, haunted faces, digital accessories, backgrounds, clothing, headwear, accessories, and colors. Kilgores differ in appearance, personality, characteristics, and rarity, with some being more rare than others.
metadata.name: Happy Kilgoreween #1
